rows.label: qst006101_msg0002
rows.name:
A story about a phantom continent...
It's like a fairy tale.

rows.label: qst006101_msg0003
rows.name:
Long, long ago, there was
a phantom continent, and on
it, a mystical kingdom.

rows.label: qst006101_msg0004
rows.name:
A mystical kingdom on a phantom
continent... It has a nice ring
to it. Fitting for me.

rows.label: qst006101_msg0005
rows.name:
However, the continent
was destroyed overnight.

rows.label: qst006101_msg0006
rows.name: What!? It vanished in a single night?

rows.label: qst006101_msg0007
rows.name:
The phantom continent
that no one knows...

rows.label: qst006101_msg0008
rows.name:
Now, the story of that
continent is engraved on the
Dalnes Stone in Temperantia.

rows.label: qst006101_msg0011
rows.name:
Hey, you're not going to believe
a fairy tale like this, are you?

rows.label: qst006101_msg0012
rows.name:
Fool! Are fairy tales not
also respectable records!

rows.label: qst006101_msg0013
rows.name:
They are left behind to convey
something. It is worth investigating!

rows.label: qst006101_msg0014
rows.name:
Come, my retainers! We
shall head to Temperantia!
